# AI Document Intelligence Platform

An AI-powered document processing platform built using FastAPI, PostgreSQL, Celery, Redis, Ollama, and Streamlit.

The platform enables users to upload documents, automatically extract text using OCR, generate AI-powered summaries, and monitor document processing through a user-friendly dashboard.

---

## Features

### Document Upload

* Upload PDF, PNG, JPG, and JPEG files
* File validation and metadata storage
* REST API powered by FastAPI

### OCR Processing

* Text extraction from PDF documents using PyMuPDF
* OCR support for images using Tesseract OCR
* Background processing using Celery workers
* Queue management using Redis

### AI-Powered Summarization

* Local LLM-based summarization using Ollama
* No dependency on external AI APIs
* Offline AI processing support

### Background Task Processing

* Asynchronous document processing using Celery
* Redis as message broker
* Non-blocking API requests

### Document Management

* Track processing status
* Store extracted text
* Store generated summaries
* View document metadata

### Dashboard

* Interactive Streamlit interface
* Upload and manage documents
* View extracted content and summaries
* Monitor document processing

