## Architecture

```text
Streamlit
    │
    ▼
 FastAPI API
    │
    ▼
 PostgreSQL
    │
    ▼
   Celery
    │
    ▼
   Redis
    │
    ▼
 OCR Service
(PyMuPDF / Tesseract)
    │
    ▼
 Ollama
(Llama 3.2)
```

